quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  16,22,"Your God is ňĻonlyňļ One God. As for those who do not believe in the Hereafter, their hearts are in denial, and they are too proud"
  16,23,"Without a doubt, Allah knows what they conceal and what they reveal. He certainly does not like those who are too proud"
  16,24,"And when it is said to them, ‚ÄúWhat has your Lord revealed?‚ÄĚ They say, ‚ÄúAncient fables!‚ÄĚ"
  16,25,Let them bear their burdens in full on the Day of Judgment as well as some of the burdens of those they mislead without knowledge. Evil indeed is what they will bear